overview: Careful cave exploration in your flying ship, watch the fuel meter and go fast enough to get to the next refueling station but watch out for the traps and lasers left around to stifle your journey. If you hit the walls or a laser beam, you will start at the screen entrance. Getting to the next screen does NOT replenish your fuel supplies, so you'd better hope the fueling station is close. A game created by Arne Jansen and Harald Beine and published in 64'er 1985/05.
